title: Brent discusses navigating his American identity while living in Asia

media:group.media:title: Brent discusses navigating his American identity while living in Asia
media:group.media:description:
Brent, a participant in our “Being Asian in America” documentary, discusses navigating his American identity while living abroad in Asia. 

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
